- Change `X` to `fmri_masked` and `y` to `target`, for consistency (and allowing all the inlined code to be copied/pasted without any trouble);
- For the same reason, defining `n_conditions = len(set(target))` manually;
- In the beginning, before downloading the data, warning about the time and size required for fetching them;
- A `classification_accuracy` was displayed `1.000`, it is misleading as a 100% accuracy is almost never achievable;
- Update displayed signature of a sklearn.svm.SVC object (eps is now called tol, default cache_size is 200 Mb).
